{
  "text": "A limitation in intellectual functioning and adaptive behavior as expressed in conceptual, social and practical adaptive skills, which originates before the age of 18. Epidemiologie unbeabsichtigter und vors\u00e4tzlicher Verletzungen bei Para-Athleten with communication, fewer meaningful relationships, and increased assistance required to navigate social and sport settings [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
